{"tid":1096661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」港龍機右引擎起火　飛機在外海盤旋洩油","createTime":"2019-04-08T00:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T00:44:32.000Z","uid":113073,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5b2982a120b3ac28865408ce7fbb1e8cabb5a882","tid":1096661,"uid":113073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T00:44:32.000Z","msg":"一架從高雄小港機場起飛的港龍航空，才剛起飛沒多久引擎發出怪異聲響，有目擊民眾表示是右引擎起火，這據了解這班是港龍451，8點2分從高雄起飛，右邊2號引擎疑似起火，起飛不久就起火，這班飛機在外海盤旋洩油後，緊急回到高雄小港機場，消防隊已經在跑道待命，引擎起火原因還有待進一步釐清。<br />\n<br />\n原文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190408/1417240.htm?from=fb_et_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190408%2F1417240.htm%3Ffrom%3Dfb_et_news&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=0919b48b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190408/1417240.htm?from=fb_et_news</a>"}]}